## What I Built
- Hub & Spoke VNet architecture with VNet Peering
- NSG-based perimeter security (replacing Azure Firewall)
- ASG micro-segmentation between workload tiers
- Azure Policy for compliance enforcement
- Custom RBAC roles implementing Least Privilege
- Time-limited role assignments (PIM equivalent)

## Design Decisions
Used NSGs instead of Azure Firewall to achieve same security 
controls within free-tier constraints. In production this would 
extend to Azure Firewall Premium + PIM.

